---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for HEK Design Studio. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-[100px] pb-24">
    <header class="mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-h2 text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-body text-text-muted">Last updated: February 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-12 text-body text-text-secondary">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          HEK Design Studio ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting
          the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
          and safeguard your information when you visit our website at hekdesign.studio.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We only collect information that you voluntarily provide through our contact form. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Company name (optional)</li>
          <li>Project details and description</li>
          <li>Budget range</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We do not automatically collect any personal information, browsing data, or analytics
          about your visit to our website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          The information you provide through our contact form is used solely to respond to your
          inquiry and discuss potential projects. We may use your email address to follow up on
          your request and communicate about the services you've expressed interest in.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use the following third-party services to operate our website:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>
            <strong class="text-white">Formspree</strong> — Processes contact form submissions.
            Your form data is transmitted to and stored by Formspree. View their
            <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white underline hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">privacy policy</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-white">Vercel</strong> — Hosts our website. View their
            <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white underline hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">privacy policy</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-white">Sanity</strong> — Content management system that stores our website content. View their
            <a href="https://www.sanity.io/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white underline hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">privacy policy</a>.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          We do not use cookies, tracking pixels, analytics services, or any other tracking
          technologies on our website. Your browsing activity is not monitored or recorded.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Form submissions are retained by Formspree according to their data retention policies.
          We may keep a copy of your inquiry in our email system for as long as necessary to
          fulfill the purpose for which it was collected or as required for business records.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal
          information we hold about you. To exercise these rights, please contact us using the
          information provided below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please
          contact us at{' '}
          <a href="mailto:hello@hekdesign.studio" class="text-white underline hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors">
            hello@hekdesign.studio
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-h3 text-white mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this
          page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
